'''Blendtec'''是[[美國|美國]]一家[[攪拌機|攪拌機]]製造商，為K-TEC公司的部門之一，創始人為[[Will_It_Blend?|Tom Dickson]]。成立於1975年，總部位於[[猶他州|猶他州]][[奧勒姆_(猶他州)|奧勒姆]]<ref name="NYT">[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/24/magazine/24wwln-consumed-t.html Mixing It Up] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/24/magazine/24wwln-consumed-t.html |date=20161229042427 }}, [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_Times New York Times], Rob Walker, August 22, 2008</ref><ref name="NYT" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.blendtec.com/company/about |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-07 |archive-date=2016-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203183845/http://www.blendtec.com/company/about |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其以系列廣告「''[[Will_It_Blend?|Will It Blend?]]''」的[[病毒式行銷|病毒式行銷]]聞名<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/05/will-it-blend/|title=Will It Blend?|last=Pogue|first=David|date=2007-01-05|work=New York Times|accessdate=2013-10-15|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104223519/http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/05/will-it-blend/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年7月，Blendtec以Blendtec Signature Series™和Stealth®攪拌機系列的創新榮獲2013年金獎創新獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.couponcodeslady.com/2013/10/blendtec-wins-gold-innovation-award-2013.html |title=Blendtec snags 2013 Gold Innovation Award |accessdate=2016-12-07 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023202231/http://www.couponcodeslady.com/2013/10/blendtec-wins-gold-innovation-award-2013.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>Blendtec也是營養品公司Blendfresh™的母公司，該公司於2014年7月14日開始運營。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.good4utah.com/story/d/story/blender-company-launches-new-products/41318/-qvbGZ3q6kidqQVwZZlAcw|title=Blender company launches new products|date=2014-07-14|publisher=ABC4|accessdate=2016-12-07|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208072047/http://www.good4utah.com/story/d/story/blender-company-launches-new-products/41318/-qvbGZ3q6kidqQVwZZlAcw|dead-url=no}}</ref>

